<p>HuazhongCNC) made a major industry impact at the 14th China CNC Machine =
Tool Exhibition (CCMT 2026), held in Shanghai from April 21 to 25, 2026. Sh=
owcasing its latest lineup of intelligent CNC systems under the theme =E2=
=80=9CFive-Axis Leadership, Generation 10 Empowerment,=E2=80=9D the company=
 demonstrated its commitment to digital, networked, and intelligent manufac=
turing =E2=80=94 and took home the coveted CCMT 2026 Spring Swallow Award.<=
/p>



<h2><strong>HuazhongCNC at CCMT 2026: A Showcase of Next-Generation Intelli=
gent Manufacturing</strong><strong></strong></h2>



<p>Booth W1-A111 drew consistent crowds throughout the five-day exhibition.=
 HNC&nbsp;CNC presented its full portfolio of intelligent CNC solutions, at=
tracting engineers, procurement managers, and executives from across the ma=
nufacturing sector. Key exhibits included:</p>



<ul>
<li>HNC10 Intelligent CNC System</li>



<li>HNC-8&nbsp;Premium Five-Axis CNC System</li>



<li>HNC8 Turning-Milling-Grinding CNC System</li>



<li>Industrial Machine Tool Forward Design Cloud Platform</li>
</ul>



<figure class=3D"wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding=3D"async" loading=
=3D"lazy" width=3D"1024" height=3D"768" src=3D"https://en.huazhongcnc.com/w=
p-content/uploads/2026/04/f-1024x768.jpg" alt=3D"" class=3D"wp-image-15843"=
 style=3D"filter: blur(4px);"></figure>



<p>Over 110 machine tools powered by HNC&nbsp;CNC systems were on display, =
jointly exhibited with leading domestic machine tool manufacturers. The mac=
hines ranged from intelligent CNC machining centers and five-axis machines =
to turning-milling compound machines and CNC lathes, with more than 30 unit=
s running the flagship HNC10 system.</p>



<figure class=3D"is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-3 wp-block-gallery has-nes=
