<h2><strong>HNC10 Intelligent CNC System: Redefining Smart Machining with a=
 1+2+3 Architecture</strong><strong></strong></h2>



<p>The HNC-10 Intelligent CNC System was the undisputed highlight of the ex=
hibition. Built on a proprietary =E2=80=9C1+2+3=E2=80=9D architecture, this=
 system represents a breakthrough in intelligent CNC technology:</p>



<h3><strong>1 Intelligent Foundation</strong><strong></strong></h3>



<p>A high-performance domestic bus interface integrated with an AI chip del=
ivers the hardware backbone required for stable, high-speed CNC operation.<=
/p>



<h3><strong>2 Digital Main Lines</strong><strong></strong></h3>



<p>Two digital threads span the full machine lifecycle =E2=80=94 from desig=
n and production to maintenance =E2=80=94 enabling seamless data connectivi=
ty and traceability across the manufacturing workflow.</p>



<h3><strong>3 Functional Subsystems</strong><strong></strong></h3>



<p>Three specialized subsystems handle process optimization, precision cont=
rol, and intelligent maintenance. Powered by a built-in industry-specific l=
arge AI model and a CNC domain knowledge graph, the HNC-10 enables machines=
 to autonomously perceive, learn, and make decisions =E2=80=94 elevating ma=
chining from digital to truly intelligent.</p>



<p><strong>Award Highlight: </strong>The HNC-10 system received the CCMT 20=
26 Spring Swallow Award, one of the most prestigious honors in China=E2=80=
=99s CNC industry, recognizing it as a breakthrough innovation reshaping th=
e future of intelligent machining =E2=80=94 dubbed =E2=80=9CChina=E2=80=99s=
 Smart Brain=E2=80=9D by industry observers.</p>



