p-content/uploads/2026/04/a1-1024x768.jpg" alt=3D"CCMT 2026" class=3D"wp-im=
age-15848" style=3D"filter: blur(4px);"></figure>



<h2><strong>HNC-8 Turning-Milling-Grinding CNC System: Versatile Precision =
for General Manufacturing</strong><strong></strong></h2>



<p>Targeting high-volume general manufacturing environments, the HNC-8 Turn=
ing-Milling-Grinding CNC System is purpose-built for the three core machini=
ng operations: turning, milling, and grinding. Key capabilities include:</p=
>



<ul>
<li>High-speed, high-frequency response characteristics for demanding produ=
ction cycles</li>



<li>Optimized control algorithms enabling precise grinding of eccentric and=
 non-circular surfaces</li>



<li>Multi-channel and synchronous control technology for flexible adaptatio=
n to turning centers and grinding machines</li>
</ul>



<p>This system is well-suited for industries including automotive component=
s and general mechanical engineering, offering manufacturers a high-perform=
ance, cost-effective, and stable CNC solution.</p>



<figure class=3D"wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding=3D"async" loading=
