<h2><strong>Machining Automation on the Show Floor: HuazhongCNC JR6210 Indu=
strial Robot</strong><strong></strong></h2>



<p>Live automation demonstrations added another dimension to the HNC&nbsp;C=
NC exhibit. The HuazhongCNC=E2=80=99s&nbsp;JR6210 Robot =E2=80=94 equipped =
with a high-power, high-speed servo motor and a lightweight body structure =
=E2=80=94 impressed visitors with its ability to handle heavy loads without=
 sacrificing agility. The design directly addresses a longstanding pain poi=
nt in industrial robotics: the trade-off between payload capacity and movem=
ent speed.</p>



